            "synopsis" : {"type" : 23, "value" : "A handful of PAD's to help explain the rules of the combat in the Undercity ruins better.\r\n\r\n- A simple comment to help emphasise that the combat is over, even though it hasn't finished yet (it'll play as they begin to \"Poof\" offstage)\r\n\r\n- The Farslayer has started casting his magic spell\r\n\r\n- Combat has started and we want the player to know there's one particularly deadly opponent - the Farslayer. "},
